/// Sentinel value returned by WorkflowContext continueAsNew: to signal
/// that the workflow should restart with fresh history and new args.
///
/// The WorkflowRunner checks the result of run:ctx: for this type and
/// delegates to the engine to create a new execution.
///
///   ContinueAsNewRequest new: #{#args => #("nextCursor")}
Value subclass: ContinueAsNewRequest
  state: args :: List = #()
